<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,505,1790]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1693,1718]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species very much resembles the European species 
<taxonomicName authority="Schiner, 1862" authorityName="Schiner" authorityYear="1862" box="[964,1284,1693,1718]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Billaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maritima">
<emphasis box="[964,1100,1694,1717]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">B. maritima</emphasis>
(Schiner, 
